snippet.title: Super Monkey Ball Banana Rumble – SEGA Pass – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Sonic, Amy, Tails, & Knuckles are on a roll as they join Super Monkey Ball Banana Rumble as part of the SEGA Pass paid DLC! Beat and Axel also join the fun, alongside 15 customization items. 
 
SEGA Pass content arrives in 2024: https://ninten.do/6052Y2HlO
